<div class="home__mid">
  <div class="message__line">
    <h2>What we aim</h2>
  </div>
  <p>                                               Our planet is facing a drastic change over the last century.
    <br class="wrap__home__mid__message__from__960">The speed of the transition is too quick for people and nature to adapt and,
    <br>                                            more than 1 million species are facing a serious issue of extinction.
    <br class="wrap__home__mid__message__from__960">Pollution continues to harm both our bodies and nature.
    <br>                                            We as a platform aim to provide a way to get out of this transformation
    <br class="wrap__home__mid__message__from__960">with connecting companies and NGOs which try to do good for the planet.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="home__video">
  <div class="video__message">
    <h2 class="message__line">Support Your NGO's <br class="wrap__message__video">environment projects</h2>
    <p>Please find our projects which are fighting for environmental targets. <br>It is one of the most crucial issues in regard to SDGs goal.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="video">
    <%# Add this at the end of the link to loop and auto play ?autoplay=1&mute=1&loop=1&playlist=<%= video_id %>
    <iframe
            <% video_id = "Np9ChlVnNlY" %>
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/<%= video_id %>"
            title="YouTube video player"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen>
    </iframe>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="home__bottom">
  <div class="bottom__display" data-controller="card">
    <div class="info__left description__position">
        <div class="card__description left__description left__description__standard">
          <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          <h5>Find you project!</h5>
          <h4>We have a wide range of projects. Let's find your favorite projects.</h4>
          <span>More detail</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card__description left__description left__description__environment">
          <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          <h5>Environment matters!</h5>
          <%= link_to "", projects_path(query: "environment"), class: "card__link__description" %>
          <h4>Our environment is facing a rapid augmentation of temperature we have never seen. Let's fight together!</h4>
          <span>More detail</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card__description left__description left__description__education">
          <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          <h5>Education is a key factor!</h5>
          <%= link_to "", projects_path(query: "education"), class: "card__link__description" %>
          <h4>In order for us to rectify the inequality in this world, education is a terrain to be addressed.</h4>
          <span>More detail</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card__description left__description left__description__culture">
          <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          <h5>Man of culture!</h5>
          <%= link_to "", projects_path(query: "culture"), class: "card__link__description" %>
          <h4>Support projects that address the crisis of cultural heritage inheritance.</h4>
          <span>More detail</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card__description left__description left__description__animal">
          <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          <h5>Help our animals!</h5>
          <%= link_to "", projects_path(query: "animal"), class: "card__link__description" %>
          <h4>We want to protect our animals and work on animal welfare. Join us on our journey.</h4>
          <span>More detail</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card__list__right">
      <h2 class="home__bottom__message message__line home__bottom__message__no__wrap">Our projects by category</h2>
      <div class="cards cards__environment" data-controller="card" data-action="click->card#environment"
                                                                   data-action-target="environment">
          <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
          <span class="link__cards card__link inner__box">Environment</span>
          <%# <%= link_to "Environment", root_path, class: "link__cards card__link first__card" %>
      </div>
      <div class="cards cards__education" data-action="click->card#education"
                                          data-action-target="education">
          <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
          <span class="link__cards card__link inner__box">Education</span>
          <%# <%= link_to "Education", root_path, class: "link__cards card__link second__card" %>
      </div>
      <div class="cards cards__culture" data-action="click->card#culture"
                                        data-action-target="culture">
          <i class="fas fa-wine-glass-alt"></i>
          <span class="link__cards card__link inner__box">Culture</span>
          <%# <%= link_to "Culture", root_path, class: "link__cards card__link third__card" %>
      </div>
      <div class="cards cards__animal" data-action="click->card#animal"
                                       data-action-target="animal">
          <i class="fas fa-otter"></i>
          <span class="link__cards card__link inner__box">Animal</span>
          <%# <%= link_to "Animal", root_path, class: "link__cards card__link forth__card" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
